Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Urban problems are universal
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407j13
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 31 Jul 1977
Problems facing urban areas are not local, but universal. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.